  (3453,'post','what-is-rcm',NULL,3424,'What is RCM?','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;What is Revenue Cycle Management?&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Exemplar Health Resources RCM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the processes and protocols to assure that physicians get paid for what they do and that they are paid in a timely fashion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #000000; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;The revenue cycle starts when the patient appointment is created and office personnel acquire the patient''s name, demographic stats, and relevant data including insurance information. The cycle ends when the balance of the patient account is zero.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; display: block; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; color: #000000; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&